      "content": "The 85% projection accounts for the observed variance by applying a conservative predictive modeling filter to the raw logs. Those \"wild swings\" you noticed are characteristic of early-stage biological response, not systemic failure, and have been mathematically smoothed out. We are confident because the *average* trend across the cohort strongly supports the projection, mitigating the impact of those individual outliers.",
